data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Sherwood Manor, nestled on the cusp of Sherwood Forest Estates. This stunning 4 Bedroom 2.5 Bathroom residence is a true masterpiece, boasting 2401 SqFt of living space. As you step inside, you're greeted by an inviting atmosphere. Formal living room is perfect for elegant gatherings, dining room sets the stage for memorable dinners and the open concept family room which  flows into the kitchen and wet bar creating a hub to gather. This property offers a private entry room to be used as a possible space for an office, in-law quarters, or rental opportunity. Located in a highly sought after Sylvan School district, your home awaits in the coveted Sherwood Manor!
